A playlist generator for playdar. The user enters an artist and a track they wish to listen to and the script generates a playlist using the Last.fm API to get similar 
tracks to the one being resolved initially. This works best with a large collection of music or a good selection of resolvers.

REQUIREMENTS
============

To run this script the following dependancies are required:

perl
mplayer

In addition to perl the following modules are utilised:

WWW::Mechanize
JSON
JSON::XS
LWP::Simple
Net::LastFM
Proc::Simple

RUN
===

To run this script use the following command:

perl playerdar.pl
